</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">показалци: [0 6]
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">[пра р]
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">[0 6 2 4]
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">[пра пка палка]
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">всички: [[0 6 2 4] [23 29 25 27] [37 47 39 45]]
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">[пра пка]
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">true
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">израз: п([а-я]+)а
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">една слива
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">една ПРАСКОВА</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>За да видите пълния справочник на редовѝте изрази,
погледнете документацията за пакета
<a href="https://pkg.go.dev/regexp"><code>regexp</code></a>.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code empty">
            
          
          </td>
        </tr>
        
      </table>
      
      
